        technicalNotes: 'Prisma migration: 3 String → Json column changes, backfill via manual SQL migration (single-file → { "Solution.<ext>": <existing> } map). server/src/services/ai.prompts.js CODE_REVIEW template accepts a file-map, XML-fences each file with a `<file name="X.java" language="java">…</file>` shape. Zod schema stays the same shape — review is per-attempt not per-file. Server sanitization applied per-file. Client: MonacoLabEditor gets an internal tab state + tab-bar UI; the parent (ConceptLabTab) manages the file-map as a JS object, not per-tab strings. LocalStorage draft value becomes JSON (schema-versioned in case we evolve the shape). New test suite: `server/test/integration/curriculum.autosave-collision.integration.test.js` (multi-tab last-writer-wins semantics + reload safety). Rough estimate: 5-6 days (2 days migration + prompt + AI validator changes, 2 days client tab bar UI + Monaco integration, 1 day tests + rollout).',
